  "prompt": "Are there pens with thick grip and thinner tip?  Is it available in India below 50 rupees?",
  "response": "Yes, there are pens available with a thick grip and thinner tip. These types of pens are designed to provide comfort while writing, making them suitable for extended use. In India, you can find various brands and models that fit this description.\n\nBrands like **Parker**, **Reynolds**, and **Cello** often offer pens that might meet your needs. Additionally, many local stationery brands also provide similar options.\n\nAs for the price, there are several pens available under 50 rupees in India. You can find them at local stationery shops, online marketplaces, or even in larger retail stores. It\u2019s a good idea to check reviews or product descriptions to ensure that the pen has the desired grip and tip size before purchasing.",
